The paper introduces a novel imitation learning algorithm that uses a game-theoretic notion of correlated equilibrium and a queue of discriminators and agents. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
